---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { CONTACT_INFO, SITE } from "../data/site";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description={`Privacy policy for ${SITE.name} — how we collect, use, and protect information when you use our website or contact us.`}
>
  <section class="bg-cream py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        How we handle information when you browse our site, send us a message, or interact with {SITE.name}.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-stone-400 mb-10">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy describes how {SITE.name} (“we,” “us,” or “our”) collects, uses, and shares information
            in connection with our website and related communications. By using our website, you agree to this policy. If
            you do not agree, please discontinue use of the site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Information we collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We may collect the following types of information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Information you provide.</strong> When you contact us (for
              example through our contact form or by email), we receive whatever details you choose to send, such as
              your name, email address, phone number, and the content of your message.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Technical data.</strong> Like many websites, our hosting and
              infrastructure may automatically log basic technical information such as your browser type, general
              location (e.g., region), referring page, and the date and time of requests. This helps us operate and
              secure the site.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Cookies and similar technologies.</strong> We may use
              cookies or similar tools that are necessary for the site to function, or that help us understand how the
              site is used in aggregate. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">How we use information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer service;</li>
            <li>Process or discuss orders, catering requests, or other business you initiate with us;</li>
            <li>Operate, maintain, and improve our website and services;</li>
            <li>Detect and help prevent fraud, abuse, or security issues;</li>
            <li>Comply with applicable law and enforce our rights.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Sharing of information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We do not sell your personal information. We may share information only in these situations:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Service providers.</strong> We may use trusted vendors to host
              our website, send email, analyze traffic, or provide similar services. They may process information only
              as needed to perform work for us and are expected to protect it appropriately.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Legal requirements.</strong> We may disclose information if
              required by law, court order, or government request, or to protect the rights, safety, or property of our
              customers, our business, or others.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong class="text-stone-800 font-medium">Business transfers.</strong> If we are involved in a merger,
              acquisition, or sale of assets, information may be transferred as part of that transaction, subject to
              appropriate safeguards.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Third-party links and embeds</h2>
          <p>
            Our site may include links to other websites or embedded content (such as maps). Those services have their
            own privacy practices. We encourage you to read their policies; we are not responsible for their content or
            practices.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">California residents</h2>
          <p>
            If you are a California resident, you may have additional rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act
            (CCPA), including the right to know what personal information we collect, to request deletion of certain
            personal information, and to opt out of the “sale” of personal information (we do not sell personal
            information as defined by the CCPA). To exercise these rights, contact us using the information below. We
            will not discriminate against you for exercising your privacy rights.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Children’s privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our website is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from
            children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us and we will take
            appropriate steps to delete it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Data security</h2>
          <p>
            We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical safeguards designed to protect the information we
            hold. No method of transmission over the internet is completely secure; we cannot guarantee absolute
            security.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain information only as long as needed for the purposes described in this policy, unless a longer
            period is required or permitted by law (for example, for tax or accounting records).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The “Last updated” date at the top will change when we
            do. Continued use of the site after changes means you accept the updated policy. We encourage you to review
            this page periodically.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Contact us</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about this Privacy Policy or your information, contact {SITE.name} at{" "}
            <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_INFO.email}`} class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark underline underline-offset-2">
              {CONTACT_INFO.email}
            </a>,{" "}
            <a href={CONTACT_INFO.phoneHref} class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark underline underline-offset-2">
              {CONTACT_INFO.phone}
            </a>, or write to us at {CONTACT_INFO.location}.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
